---
title: Honey-Glazed Indian Chicken with Roast Veggie & Crispy Flatbread Salad
description: Can’t decide between sweet or savoury, don’t worry we couldn’t either so we combined it into one! Tender chicken
is cooked in our Mumbai spice blend and then baked in a layer of honey. You won’t have to worry about picking one
flavour over the other again with this recipe under your belt.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

